content.text:
Here's an improved version with several enhancements:

```css
/* Reset and base styles */
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #333;
  background-color: #fff;
}

/* Container for centered content */
.container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1rem;
  width: 100%;
}

/* Responsive adjustments */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  body {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .container {
    padding: 0 0.75rem;
  }
}
```

## Key Improvements:

✅ **`box-sizing: border-box`** - Makes width/padding calculations easier across all elements

✅ **Typography** - Added system font stack, font-size, line-height, and default color for better readability

✅ **Container centering** - Added `margin: 0 auto` and `width: 100%` to properly center the container

✅ **Horizontal padding** - Added padding to .container for mobile-friendly spacing

✅ **Smooth scrolling** - Added to html element for better UX

✅ **Responsive design** - Adjusts font size and padding on smaller screens

✅ **Color defaults** - Set background and text colors for consistency

Would you like me to add anything else, like:
- Additional color variables/themes?
- Interactive element styles (buttons, links)?
- More sophisticated responsive breakpoints?
- CSS custom properties (variables) for maintainability?

